The problem you got is related to use maven-embedder inside a shade/fatjat/jarwithdependencies

When you create the jar-with-dependencies, some resources may be defined in many jars but only one is packed inside the jar (the last one processed). Here is where the problem lays with the ```META-INF/plexus/components.xml``` and ```META-INF/sisu/javax.inject.Named``` files required by Maven and Plexus

